#. type: Plain text
#: site/content/en/faq.md
msgid ""
"Marking all individual files with `SPDX-License-Identifier` tags goes a long "
"way towards unambiguously communicating the license information of your "
"project, but it helps to communicate the license information in natural "
"language as well. In the README of your project, feel free to provide a "
"summary of the licensing information, or simply redirect the reader to your "
