"The `reuse download` command enables you to download a specific license. "
"`reuse download GPL-3.0-or-later` would fulfil the task described in the "
"manual instructions above. Running `reuse download --all` automatically "
"downloads all licenses which the REUSE helper tool detects as being used in "
"your project."
